    Scope and Contents
The Dean of Business &amp; Administrative Services Housing files includes material regarding the Student Housing Cooperative, lease agreement, Developers/Realtors, surveys, housing applications, the Streetside Boosters, Rudolph's Bean (People's Place) Coffee House, the Peer Counseling program, and the Housing Act Part I &amp; II.  It also includes a progress report on Capital Program and Roof Moisture Survey Report.  
  
